company_name: MEIKO KONSERVENFABRIK FRANZ MEIER GMBH & CO. KG
information: The company MEIKO KONSERVENFABRIK FRANZ MEIER GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1953, which operates in the Fish industry. It also operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industries. It is based in Osterhofen, Germany.
